{"tid":2389133,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"麗港城居民喊「加油」警方一度「抬走」男子調查","createTime":"2021-01-31T15:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T19:38:14.000Z","uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d11c28969ba03e790da4f93c80662be34c6223","tid":2389133,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"【31/1 麗港城居民喊「加油」警方一度「抬走」男子調查 】<br />\n<br />\n下午8時許，有一名男子於麗港城5座外高叫，其後亦有其他人士叫「5座加油」及「7座加油」口號，有數名警員上前要求不要叫囂，又詢問該名男子是否居民，該名男子表示「居民」及高呼「佢(警員)叫我唔好講野」，隨即有警員稱「捉佢」，另一名警員亦向男子呼喝「先生，出黎!」並上前要求帶走。<br />\n<br />\n帶走其間該名男子曾稱「好驚」及「就暈」於第二次跌倒時有警員上前「抬腳」帶到室內坐下。<br />\n<br />\n其後，該男子以涉嫌「公眾地方行為不檢」被帶上警車前往警署。<br />\n<br />\n攝:何零解<br />\n__<br />\nPa treon月付會員制:(pshk_media_offical)<br />\nM e w e : photographicsocietyhk<br />\n訂閱 Y o u t u b e : PSHK media official<br />\nIG : pshkinc<br />\n官方網站 : Pshk.pro<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JH8XOx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JH8XOx.jpg&h=6cec4639&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmTTptx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkmTTptx.jpg&h=0c2de88d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJ2T8Vd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJ2T8Vd.jpg&h=e8a04c28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HDW6GU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HDW6GU.jpg&h=a072188a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c33d15771cd0409a2a459f9d5834cd7dbcda18e","tid":2389133,"uid":362827,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"私人地方黎架喎"},{"pid":"73901e65cd66072f8d3472becd926b4eb5cb9e77","tid":2389133,"uid":201637,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"嗌加油都拉 做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa